{"tid":1722861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨做野了","createTime":"2019-11-15T04:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:16:19.000Z","uid":132326,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9dcd2da20cbb70a2a3c6e08e0c7b6bd21177dee","tid":1722861,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span></span></strong> 係佢地老本行<br />\n<br />\n你唔需要係當事人，只需要話畀你知有分化情況發生，再畀佢地各自立場你，人好自然就會揀其中一個立場。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">結果：你已經被分化</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例：鄭承隆記者會。提出<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">區選</span></strong>，因為共黨知道香港人其中一個最大分歧係放唔放棄區選，有好多人已經唔信制度，所以有冇區選都冇所謂；但無可否認地，有好多好多人都覺得要體制內外都要試。透過喺中大起大台，用示威者身份提出 區選不能延期 呢個分歧，全世界都好自然會揀一個立場：你已經被分化了。因為區選延唔延期係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></strong>既決定，唔係示威者決定，所以「區選延期與否」係偽命題。<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖係佢喺大台上面講出呢個term，已經可以有分化效果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f7efd02ac8a4b0ac97ce711c9a230e67e980fd","tid":1722861,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"叫親成龍嘅都係仆街冚家鏟啦㗎屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3303b79d26056f5b74bcfe4c8090fad0742f903a","tid":1722861,"uid":29787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"長期留守一定會有分化出現，守唔過，一晚中大已不攻自破，重開左路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91f4bd6752a6db379bb1a81290f6b72d2e3e705","tid":1722861,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"大大個國民黨都分化到散<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64ef94127443516d3f34150a6cd2fb5d1ca96f2","tid":1722861,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b91f4bd6752a6db379bb1a81290f6b72d2e3e705","tid":1722861,"